data.description: Welcome home! This home is less than 4 years old and still looks new. It is beautiful, clean, and well maintained. The location is minutes from everything Rockmart has to offer including restaurants, schools, parks, shopping, and entertainment. As you walk through the front door, the entry way is open and spacious, the perfect space to have all of your coats and kids bookbags in an accessible location. The open concept kitchen and living room boast an electric fireplace with plenty of room for entertaining or relaxing. The kitchen has new stainless steel appliances and a garbage disposal. Walk up the stairs to a second living room, 4 bedrooms, laundry room and 2 full baths. The master suite includes its own sitting area and en suite with a separate walk in shower and soaking tub. Don't miss out on this one!!
